news_header: Trump attacks Zelensky, calling him a dictator, prompting backlash from European leaders amid ongoing Ukraine-Russia tensions.
news_original_title: Trump calls Zelensky a 'dictator' as rift between two leaders deepens
news_text: President Trump criticized Ukraine's President Zelensky, labeling him a dictator, which led to backlash from European leaders. Zelensky emphasized the importance of constructive US cooperation.
